*******************************************************************************
       Name: Convergence Shield
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_CHAR_SELF
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 100
 Wait Beats: 12
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: Your convergence shield dissipates.
Acquisition:
   - Grand Magi: level 8
Description:
   Convergence Shield creates a rotating barrier of elemental forces around
   the caster, providing an AC bonus that scales with Grand Magi level and
   Intelligence.

   Duration: level / 8 hours
   AC modifier: -(Grand Magi level * 5 + Intelligence / 2)
   Mana cost: 100

   This reflects the Solar Court's original ceremonial purpose of
   "demonstrating stability under pressure" -- showing that multiple
   elemental forces can be held in organized simultaneous expression.
   Distinct from Elemental Ward (which provides saving throw reduction);
   Convergence Shield provides direct AC protection.
*******************************************************************************
